3 SECTION 2.(d) G.S. 58-58-330(a) reads as rewritten:
4 "(a) This Part does not apply to solicitations or sales involving:involving any of the
5 following:
6 …
7 (7) Contracts used to fund:fund any of the following:
8 …
9 f. Prearranged funeral contracts.contracts or transportation protection
